snippet: This fall, Square will begin processing credit and debit card transactions at Starbucks stores in the United States.
abstract: Mobile payment start-up Square forms a partnership with the Starbucks Coffee Company in which it will begin processing all credit and debit card transaction at all United States stores; Starbucks's adoption of the technology will likely catapult mobile payments into the mainstream.

byline.contributor: Brian X. Chen contributed reporting from New York.

lead_paragraph: This fall, Square will begin processing credit and debit card transactions at Starbucks stores in the United States.
